OL,5, Firms hit by a sharp surge in energy   
OL,6, prices are expected to get government  
OL,7, help worth hundreds of millions of     
OL,8, pounds, the BBC understands.           
OL,10,FGlass, ceramic and paper manufacturers 
OL,11,Fhave warned that rising prices may mean
OL,12,Fthey have to charge customers more.    
OL,14,FOn Monday, business Secretary Kwasi    
OL,15,FKwarteng submitted a formal proposal   
OL,16,Fasking the Treasury to help such firms.
OL,18,FThe Department for Business expects the
OL,19,Fprime minister to back its proposals,  
OL,20,Fwhich could involve state-backed loans.
